docs/deprecated.md
     1вҶ’# Deprecated вҖҰ
   227вҶ’## Removed вҖҰ
   229вҶ’### Short option flag longer than a single character
   231вҶ’Short option flags like `-ws` were never supported, but the old README did not make this clear. The README now states that short options are a single character.
   232вҶ’
   233вҶ’- README updated in Commander v3.
   234вҶ’- Deprecated from Commander v9.
   235вҶ’- Throws an exception in Commander v13. Deprecated and gone!
   236вҶ’- Replacement added in Commander v13.1 with support for dual long options, like `--ws, --workspace`.
   237вҶ’
